Event.info: OSINT - StalinLocker Deletes Your Files Unless You Enter the Right Code

Object.description: File object describing a file with meta-information
Object.name: file

Attribute.value: A new in-development screenlocker/wiper called StalinLocker, or StalinScreamer, was discovered by MalwareHunterTeam that gives you 10 minutes to enter a code or it will try to delete the contents of the drives on the computer. While running, it will display screen that shows Stalin while playing the USSR anthem and displaying a countdown until files are deleted.
